## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Fix |
|---|---|
| `GOOGLE_API_KEY is not set` | Export the key or add it to `.env` |
| `ModuleNotFoundError` | Run `pip install -r requirements.txt` inside the venv |
| `FileNotFoundError: knowledge_base.json` | Run from the project root directory |
| Slow first startup | Normal — embedding model downloading (~90 MB) |
| `torch` fails on Windows | `pip install torch --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu` |

---

